              <h3 class="title"><a name="id2349982"/>Mithral Golem<a href="img/EpicMonsters(G-W).Golem.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/EpicMonsters(G-W).Golem.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></h3>
